es provide a genomic record of historical tolerance to viral infection in bats. Finally, we found and experimentally validated bat-specific variation in microRNAs, which may regulate bat-specific gene-expression programs. Our reference-quality bat genomes provide the resources required to uncover and validate the genomic basis of adaptations of bats, and stimulate new avenues of research that are directly relevant to human health and disease1.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Jebb, David", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Huang, Zixia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pippel, Martin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hughes, Graham M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lavrichenko, Ksenia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Devanna, Paolo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Winkler, Sylke", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jermiin, Lars S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Skirmuntt, Emilia C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Katzourakis, Aris", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Burkitt-Gray, Lucy", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ray, David A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sullivan, Kevin A. M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Roscito, Juliana G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kirilenko, Bogdan M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "D\u00e1valos, Liliana M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Corthals, Angelique P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Power, Megan L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jones, Gareth", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ransome, Roger D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dechmann, Dina K. N.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Locatelli, Andrea G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Puechmaille, S\u00e9bastien J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fedrigo, Olivier", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Jarvis, Erich D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hiller, Michael", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Vernes, Sonja C.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Myers, Eugene W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Teeling, Emma C.", "affiliation"